title.narrative: 3FM Serious Request 2015: The Next Generation, Philippines

description.narrative: The Red Cross supports the development of young people in war and conflict by focussing on four different area's: education and personal development, psychosocial support, food and income for families, and emergency assistance as well as response preparedness
The aim of the programme is to make young people who have to cope with conflict and that are part of ‘this next generation’ more resilient to the consequences of conflict.
The project will focus on young people coping with war and conflict.
The project will take place in the Philippines, Surigao del Norte
This project is funding the development of a project proposal on ‘Support on Development of Youth’ in the Philippines.
